&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err-http1-header-parsing/"&gt;ERR_HTTP1_HEADER_PARSING&lt;/a&gt; — header parsing failed.&lt;/li&gt;
