&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err_http_invalid_chunk/"&gt;ERR_HTTP_INVALID_CHUNK&lt;/a&gt; — invalid chunked encoding.&lt;/li&gt;
